lingual, digital classroom.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 17. Dez 2021) 0aLanguage and languagesxComputer-assisted instruction. 0aMultilingual education. 7aEDUCATION / Computers & Technology.2bisacsh  aCALL.  aMCALL.  aPlurilingualism.  aSLA.  acomputer-assisted language learning.  adigital language learning and teaching.  alanguage learning and computer games.  alanguage teaching with computers .  alanguage teaching with technology.  amultilingualism.  amultiliteracies.  atechnology in the classroom.1 aAlm, Antonie, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAlvarez, John Michael, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBrunsmeier, Sonja, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBuendgens-Kosten, Judith, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aCoyle, Do, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDausend, Henriette, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aElsner, Daniela, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aElsner, Daniela, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aHallet, Wolfgang, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKolb, Annika, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKosten, Judith Buendgens-, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMeier, Gabriela, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMeyer, Oliver, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPfeifer, Sílvia Melo-, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPohl, Manuela, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSchmid, Euline Cutrim, econtributor.4c